['Top 3 Reasons To Join Us Opportunity to be trained and work in EU & Asia
Attractive salary and bonuses (13th month + bonus)
Premium healthcare package, Free language courses', "Job Description About the project:
Our Hanoi agency is currently looking for a 'jack-of-all-trades' type of person or professionals that can take on the Python Developers/ Technical Leader/ Scrum Master role(s).

You will join an Agile-driven team to produce and implement functional software solutions. 
About Pentalog:
As a leading European Software Services company operating internationally in France, Romania, Germany, Poland, Moldova, UK, Vietnam, Mexico, and the USA, we employ over 1,200 engineers and IT experts who work in a very dynamic, multicultural working environment.
At Pentalog, your talents & ambitions are recognized and rewarded; we offer plenty of opportunities to develop as an individual, as well as a professional, and we reward our collaborators who understand the importance of self-improvement.", 'Your Skills and Experience Job requirements:
For the Python Developer role:
2+ years experience coding in Python;
Solid experience in working with Python 3.8 and Django 2;
Good understanding of MySQL, Linux, Docker, NGINX, RESTful APIs, Git;
Knowledge of Sentry, Celery Flower, Jenkins CI is an advantage;
Good teamwork skills, high collaboration, and continuous learning.
Ability to communicate clearly in English.
For the Technical leader/Scrum Master role: 
Solid experience with 5+ years experience in Python and Golang;
Experience in working with Agile/Scrum methodology;
Good management skills, communication, and problem-solving skills;
Excellent command of the English language.
Extra skills:
French is a definite plus.
 ', "Why You'll Love Working Here Benefits:
